<br>
Taylor has sketched out the outline of a plan to drop the stuff into the Sun.  Another option would be burning it in a set of internationally managed reactors designed to be inherently safe with extremely low power density and a non-fertile matrix.<br>
<br>
Another way would be burning it in an accelerator  driven system, similar to the Energy Amplifier.<br>
